<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 01:54:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Kraken 部署 AI 后裁员 150 人； IPO 可能推迟至 2027 年</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/kraken-cuts-150-workers-after-deploying-ai-ipo-may-slip-to-2027</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，全球最古老的加密货币交易所之一 Kraken 已裁员以降低成本，并且由于数字资产价格大幅下跌，Kraken 可能不会像最初预期的那样尽快上市。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iIHcsH.4r5jA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 18:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/kraken-cuts-150-workers-after-deploying-ai-ipo-may-slip-to-2027</guid></item><item><title>加密货币在具有里程碑意义的立法上的胜利重塑了与银行的竞争</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/crypto-s-win-on-landmark-legislation-reshapes-rivalry-with-banks</link><description>多年来，大银行一直致力于将加密货币排除在主流金融之外，理由包括洗钱、欺诈和稳定性风险等各种问题，并认为如果没有银行同等的监管，该行业就无法享受银行般的特权。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRuS46AYKU1U/v3/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 17:07:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/crypto-s-win-on-landmark-legislation-reshapes-rivalry-with-banks</guid></item><item><title>CME、ICE 敦促美国遏制加密货币石油交易新贵</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/cme-ice-push-us-to-curb-crypto-s-offshore-oil-trading-upstart</link><description>洲际交易所和芝商所正在敦促美国控制 Hyperliquid，这是一个快速增长且不受监管的加密平台，交易所表示可能会扭曲全球油价并被用于操纵价格。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iITwUdbypwk0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 12:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/cme-ice-push-us-to-curb-crypto-s-offshore-oil-trading-upstart</guid></item><item><title>由于通胀担忧打击风险资产，比特币跌破 79,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/bitcoin-dips-below-79-000-as-inflation-fears-hit-risk-assets</link><description>由于对通货膨胀和高油价的担忧令投资者感到不安，股票等风险资产的抛售席卷了加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUMafSsucPlw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 14:36:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-15/bitcoin-dips-below-79-000-as-inflation-fears-hit-risk-assets</guid></item></channel></rss>